ZH: 这群人故意毁坏了城市公园的花坛。
EN: This group of people deliberately destroyed the flower beds in the city park.

ZH: 小偷毁坏了商店的橱窗。
EN: The thief damaged the shop's display window.

ZH: 士兵们在打击敌人的同时也毁坏了很多农田。
EN: The soldiers, while attacking the enemy, also damaged many farmlands.

ZH: 不要毁坏自然资源，我们要保护环境。
EN: Do not destroy natural resources, we need to protect the environment.

ZH: 暴风雨毁坏了这座房子的屋顶。
EN: The storm damaged the roof of this house.

ZH: 这个国家的战争毁坏了数以万计的家庭。
EN: The war in this country has destroyed thousands of families.

ZH: 请不要毁坏这些历史文物，它们有着重要的价值。
EN: Please do not destroy these historical relics, they have important value.

ZH: 没有人知道是谁毁坏了这座雕塑。
EN: No one knows who damaged this sculpture.

ZH: 这种病毒毁坏了受感染者的免疫系统。
EN: This virus destroys the immune system of the infected.

ZH: 落叶松林被山火毁坏了一半。
EN: Half of the pine forest was destroyed by the wildfire.

ZH: 让我们一起努力，不要毁坏我们的友谊。
EN: Let's work together and not destroy our friendship.

ZH: 这场飓风毁坏了整个海岸线的房屋。
EN: The hurricane destroyed houses along the entire coastline.

ZH: 这个人对他人的信任被毁坏了。
EN: This person's trust in others has been destroyed.

ZH: 我们应该制定更加严格的规定，以阻止破坏者毁坏公共财产。
EN: We should create stricter regulations to prevent vandals from damaging public property.

ZH: 虐待动物是一种不道德的行为，它会毁坏我们的道德观。
EN: Animal cruelty is an unethical behavior that damages our moral values.

ZH: 爆炸毁坏了这座大楼的结构。
EN: The explosion damaged the structure of this building.

ZH: 请不要毁坏这座美丽的庭院，它经过了很多劳动才建成。
EN: Please do not destroy this beautiful courtyard, it took a lot of effort to build.

ZH: 这种恶劣的学习环境会毁坏学生的学习热情。
EN: This poor learning environment will damage students' enthusiasm for learning.

ZH: 数百年的雕像被岁月的侵蚀所毁坏。
EN: Centuries-old statues have been damaged by the erosion of time.

ZH: 礼仪的缺失会毁坏人与人之间的关系。
EN: The lack of manners can damage relationships between people.
